Package com.mbdr.utils.parsing

package com.mbdr.utils.parsing
  • Interface Summary
    Interface
    Description
    DefeasibleParser<T extends DefeasibleFormulaCollection>
    This is the Generic class interface to be shared by all parsers that read in knowledge base text files and return DefeasibleFormulaCollections, which serve as the basis for DefeasibleKnowledgeBases.
  • Class Summary
    Class
    Description
    FileReader
    Class to provide all file reading utilities needed for reading in knowledge bases represented in "formula per line format"
    KnowledgeBaseReader
    Class provides ability to read in defeasible knowledge base text files stored in a formula per line format and returns an instance of the DefeasibleKnowledgeBase class
    Parsing
    Class to provide all parsing utilities needed for reading in knowledge bases represented in "formula per line format"
    QueryReader
    Class used for reading in query set files in which each line of the text file is expected to contain a query in the form of a single formula
